{"tid":734143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[紅毛泥封西]有建造業人士指香港錯失填海資源　有人倡填平吐露港","createTime":"2018-07-08T11:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T00:59:19.000Z","uid":51271,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e52035875a9877c3c84d9ea6decaba1707cb79","tid":734143,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405822-20180708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405822-20180708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=P6DFhhrysyAqzYA7sKiOr5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=199e02a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405822-20180708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6b829318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405822-20180708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n土地供應專責小組成員出席建造業議會為從業員舉辦的諮詢會，聽取業界對土地供應的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n多名建造業從業員支持盡快研究填海，認為香港每年有九成建築廢料運到公眾填料庫，其中絕大部分被運到台山作填海用途，認為香港錯失有關資源，應用作本地填海。<br />\n<br />\n有業界人士認為吐露港用途不大，可以整個填平；亦有人認為政府需要加快現有程序，才能釋放土地。<br />\n<br />\n出席諮詢會的專責小組主席黃遠輝表示，如果沒有經過公眾諮詢或修改法定程序，恐怕未能因為土地短缺而繞過城規會、環評報告等改劃用途的程序。他估計，即使把程序簡化加速，都不相信一個原本要花15、20年的程序變成5或10年。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老母個臭西都無用啦，不如用紅毛泥封左佢</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b5e05bca7ca009df2d0d71c019ab1472f049e04b","tid":734143,"uid":51271,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T11:23:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>停收新移民，樓價必跌</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"17d7035620497da4ed27e53c9ce205bd203181f7","tid":734143,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e861c17ea4e3f5cec51b45d32d62139442c58284","tid":734143,"uid":117200,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"建造業班人只要有錢分，你叫佢摌埋佢條村佢都肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f33f34612f3c2a5464faaa7bbd7d20891fe9af","tid":734143,"uid":192190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405822-20180708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405822-20180708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=P6DFhhrysyAqzYA7sKiOr5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=199e02a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405822-20180708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6b829318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405822-20180708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n土地供應專責小組成員出席建造業議會為從業員舉辦的諮詢會，聽取業界對土地供應的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n多名建造業從業員支持盡快研究填海，認為香港每年有九成建築廢料運到公眾填料庫，其中絕大部分被運到台山作填海用途，認為香港錯失有關資源，應用作本地填海。<br />\n<br />\n有業界人士認為吐露港用途不大，可以整個填平；亦有人認為政府需要加快現有程序，才能釋放土地。<br />\n<br />\n出席諮詢會的專責小組主席黃遠輝表示，如果沒有經過公眾諮詢或修改法定程序，恐怕未能因為土地短缺而繞過城規會、環評報告等改劃用途的程序。他估計，即使把程序簡化加速，都不相信一個原本要花15、20年的程序變成5或10年。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老母個臭西都無用啦，不如用紅毛泥封左佢</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n有錢收佢封完個老母閪再起埋個冬菇亭都仲得呀"},{"pid":"0f69872a7e589d8972eee064b42e0060f3cdd73c","tid":734143,"uid":27458,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"最好填左珠江口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef99e006f570b529cef9b1d95a14fbf327a386bc","tid":734143,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"幾時填埋維港？"},{"pid":"f91547a305535bc26431d126b3bba428b1d5c974","tid":734143,"uid":20227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"276d6e21aba94a48a9504f3fe51ca79fe